What you need to know:

NCPB Managing Director, Joseph Kimote said their working arrangement will see the cereals body use its wide network and reach to distribute the product on behalf of Soil Health Ltd. Bio-fertilisers, which are touted to improve availability of plant minerals to the roots through association, are free living bio-organisms that fix nutrients in the soil.It is also held to be able to condition the soil, improve the soil structure and texture and is non-toxic. 